      <h1 class="heading-xlarge">Roadmap</h1>

      <h2 class="heading-medium">October to December 2017</h2>
      <ul class="list list-bullet">
      <li>Self-service user management and usage reports</li>
      <li>Cost calculator</li>
      <li>Elasticsearch and Redis – private beta</li>
      <li>Private (non-internet-facing) applications*</li>
      <li>logging and monitoring – discovery/alpha</li>
      </ul>


      <h2 class="heading-medium">2018</h2>
      <ul class="list list-bullet">
      <li>UK-based GOV.UK PaaS instance</li>
      <li>RabbitMQ</li>
      <li>Logging and monitoring – public beta</li>
      <li>Billing portal</li>
      <li>Private Docker images</li>
      <li>VM isolation*</li>
      <li>File storage</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
      * dependent on upstream developments by Cloud Foundry Foundation
